OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1776280294
OL,3,CJail for stalker who suffocated woman
OL,4,Cand threatened to kill her
OL,6,FA man from Wiltshire has been jailed
OL,7,Ffor stalking a woman and suffocating
OL,8,Fher.
OL,10,FKyle Chisholm, 27, from Hilperton, was
OL,11,Fsentenced to four years and two months
OL,12,Fat Swindon Crown Court, after pleading
OL,13,Fguilty to his crimes.
OL,15,FBetween December 2023 and November
OL,16,F2025, Chisholm stalked a woman known
OL,17,Fto him and on at least two occasions
OL,18,Fcaused her to fear that violence would
OL,19,Fbe used against her.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
