FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1776280294
OL,3,CJail for stalker who suffocated woman
OL,4,Cand threatened to kill her
OL,6,FIn a statement read to the court to
OL,7,Fdescribe the impact of Chisholm's
OL,8,Factions, the survivor said: "I have
OL,9,Favoided texts from my loved ones, as I
OL,10,Fdon't like my phone anymore, I hate my
OL,11,Fphone going off, every time it's a
OL,12,Freminder of what I had to put up with.
OL,14,F"I spend a big portion of my day
OL,15,Fthinking about what is going through
OL,16,Fhis mind, for example if he is
OL,17,Fthinking about me or how obsessed he
OL,18,Fis with the thought of hurting me
OL,19,Fagain.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1776280294
OL,3,CJail for stalker who suffocated woman
OL,4,Cand threatened to kill her
OL,6,FShe added: "It consumes my thoughts
OL,7,Fand it destroys my energy and capacity
OL,8,Fto want to do anything productive or
OL,9,Fleave the house."
OL,11,FChisholm was also given an indefinite
OL,12,Frestraining order.
OL,14,FLocal Crime Investigator Ben Hillier
OL,15,Ffrom the Volume Crime Team said, "This
OL,16,Fwas a deeply distressing case
OL,17,Finvolving persistent stalking and a
OL,18,Fserious assault, which left the victim
OL,19,Ffearing for her safety. The offender's
OL,20,Fbehaviour was controlling, dangerous
OL,21,Fand wholly unacceptable.
OL,26,@wD@bOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,440,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1776280294
OL,3,CJail for stalker who suffocated woman
OL,4,Cand threatened to kill her
OL,6,F"I welcome the court's sentence, which
OL,7,Freflects the seriousness of these
OL,8,Foffences and the significant harm
OL,9,Fcaused. I would also like to commend
OL,10,Fthe victim for her courage in coming
OL,11,Fforward and supporting the
OL,12,Finvestigation.
OL,14,F"Wiltshire Police is committed to
OL,15,Ftackling stalking and violence against
OL,16,Fwomen and girls, and we will continue
OL,17,Fto take robust action against those
OL,18,Fwho seek to cause harm."
OL,26,@zD@XO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
